column5: Here are a few shots of the boys fishing weekend up north.  The weather and fishing were great.

Not bad at all.  The bald guy caught a nice pig.  You know what they say, unlucky with hair...lucky with cards...or is it fish...O crap, those bald dudes got the shaft! **kidding**  Where abouts up north were you guys?
Everyone is smiling...that's a good thing.
We were on Lake of Bays near Bracebridge/Huntsville.  By the way ....... I am the bald guy!
MEDIC!!!! We need a foot extraction specialist!  Thanks for the report bud....nice fish there.
Nice fish!  was a great week to go away!  Maureen
Short and sweet report.  The pics tell the story!  Looks like a great guys getaway weekend.
No problem man.  Bald works well for me.
Nice fish, looks like you guys had a ton of fun. WTG   Daniel
